<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">77倍速算法，77与某数相乘时，先将某数除以13为首商，扩大1000倍后，再加一个首商，最后加上余数与77的积，即为其积。可用公式</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">(13n+a)×77=n×1000+n+a×77</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">进行速算，其中某数为13n+a（n为任意正整数，a为等于、大于零而小于13的整数）。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">77×29=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 77×29</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=2×1000+2+3×77</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=2002+231</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=2233</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>